Modifications
-------------

This port has been modified from the upstream source. Material
deviations and ours-only additions are catalogued in:

    docs/references/symphony-upstream-drift.md (repo root)

Common categories of modification include: a `LocalShell` agent runner
adapter (codex-independent), additional tracker adapters
(`local_markdown`, `github_issues`, `noop`), an Anthropic LLM provider,
ECS-jsonl logging via `Symphony.Logging`, OTLP tracing, a startup
orphan-process reaper, and a dotted-key configuration shape for
fields not yet on the upstream typed schema.

